reviewText: Good film clip on Project Aphrodite. Drones still equate to death by robot.
Excellent documentary well worth the cover price for the rare footage alone.  Some great material on the 8th Air Force's secret Aphrodite missions.

We recorded the 2 hour special that has both Weird Weapons (Allies and Axis).  My seven-year-old son loves it!  He has watched it 3 times in the past week.  History did an amazing job on this special!
